<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Hyun_Bin" title="Hyun Bin">Hyun Bin</a> as Lee Chung<sup id="cite_ref-cast_7-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-cast-7">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>- the current heir to the Joseon throne, who is arrogant and only wants to marry a girl to accompany to China</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Jang_Dong-gun" title="Jang Dong-gun">Jang Dong-gun</a> as Kim Ja-joon<sup id="cite_ref-8" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-8">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>- the corrupt Minister of War who leads the Royal Family into beleiving Lee Chung is not the heir</li></ul>
