<li><a href="/wiki/Lee_Sun-bin_(actress)" title="Lee Sun-bin (actress)">Lee Sun-bin</a> as Deok-hee<sup id="cite_ref-9" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-9">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>- an archer and the second protector of Jemulpo who lee Chung has a crush on, who hits with high precision</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Seo_Ji-hye" title="Seo Ji-hye">Seo Ji-hye</a> as Concubine Jo- the princess of Joseon and sister of Lee Chung</li>
<li>Jo Dal-hwan as Monk Dae-gil- the third protector of Jemulpo, who follows Buddhist religion</li>
